      <title>贸易战使1200万吨美国作物的销售受到威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trade-war-leaves-12-million-tons-of-us-crop-sales-under-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国和加拿大已经反对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税和对更多报复的担忧，农业贸易商现在正在关注可能取消合同的潜在取消，这些合同将使大约1200万吨美国作物销售处于危险之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trade-war-leaves-12-million-tons-of-us-crop-sales-under-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 20:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
